Package ca.openosp.openo.integration.fhir.model

Class Sender

java.lang.Object
ca.openosp.openo.integration.fhir.model.Sender
public class Sender extends Object
A class that references a message senders header information. This Object builds a FHIR MessageSourceComponent

Future intentions of this class is for it to auto populate specific data according to its environment. For instance grabbing data from the OscarProperties settings.
